# No committed plan files

Do **not** commit planning or brainstorm artifacts to this repository.

- Keep plans locally under `docs/plans/` (gitignored) or outside the repo
- Keep brainstorm/requirements drafts under `docs/brainstorms/` (gitignored) or outside the repo
- Do not add `docs/plans/**` or `docs/brainstorms/**` in commits, PRs, or release trees
- Implementation work, tests, and user-facing docs belong in the repo; ce-plan / ce-brainstorm outputs do not

If a plan was committed by mistake, remove it from the branch and ensure `.gitignore` still covers those paths.
